::Cledar/Forrior/Blyer/Firearm::

Blyer, in his jet mode, approaches the ship where the IGL was to be held at, activating his comm.

"Hello, this is Blyer from the Maximals. Me and my group missed the official sign-up, but we were wondering if we could sign up late? There are three of us."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm gets partway to the IGL, reaching the ocean and starting to fly over it.
